`git-corner`
`display a quick link with styling to a repo to help with contributions`

Attributes:

  * `source` {`string`} - source to point to

  * `alt` {`string`} - alt text

  * `corner` {`boolean`} - Whether or not to be rendered in the top corner, common on tech sites

  * `size` {`string`} - basic size adjustment
